---
import Header from "./ui/Header.astro";
import ProjectItem from "./ui/ProjectItem.astro";
---

<main id="projects" class="h-screen pt-2 lg:pt-4">
  <Header label="Experience" />
  <div
    class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-around items-center mx-0 lg:mx-4 mt-4 lg:mt-10"
  >
    <ProjectItem
      role="Mobile App Developer"
      label="Feats"
      tech1="React Native"
      tech2="Jest"
      tech3="API Rest"
      customStyle="-translate-x-1 lg:translate-x-0"
    >
      <p class="lg:text-[1vw] hidden lg:block">
        I co-founded this startup, which is a social network for artists. In
        addition to overseeing the product, I was also responsible for
        developing the application itself in React Native:
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm lg:hidden">
        I co-founded a startup that serves as a social network for artists,
        where I not only led the product but also developed the application in
        React Native. My work focused on building scalable, reusable components
        and implementing custom hooks to manage business logic and state
        efficiently.
      </p>
      <ul class="lg:text-[1vw] list-disc ml-8 mt-2 hidden lg:block">
        <li>
          Creation and optimization of reusable components to improve project
          scalability.
        </li>
        <li>
          Implementation of custom hooks to manage business logic and state.
        </li>
        <li>
          Integration with REST APIs, data handling, and efficient consumption
          of external services.
        </li>
        <li>
          Design and layout of responsive screens, ensuring user experience and
          visual consistency.
        </li>
        <li>
          Collaboration with the backend and design teams to ensure an agile and
          efficient development workflow.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </ProjectItem>
    <ProjectItem
      role="Fullstack Developer"
      label="OasisVive"
      tech1="Nestjs"
      tech2="Astro"
      tech3="Tailwindcss"
      customStyle="mt-4 lg:mt-0 translate-x-1 lg:translate-x-0"
    >
      <p class="lg:text-[1vw] hidden lg:block">
        Developed a high-performance real estate website, delivering:
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm lg:hidden">
        Developed a high-performance real estate website with a responsive Figma
        UI, a NestJS REST API for dynamic property management, and Cloudinary
        media hosting. Built with Astro for lightning-fast load times and strong
        SEO, and styled with Tailwind CSS for clean, maintainable, and scalable
        design.
      </p>
      <ul class="lg:text-[1vw] list-disc ml-8 mt-2 hidden lg:block">
        <li>A fully responsive UI in Figma, optimized for all devices.</li>
        <li>
          A NestJS REST API for dynamic property management, with media hosted
          on Cloudinary.
        </li>
        <li>
          An Astro frontend achieving lightning-fast load times and strong SEO
          performance, boosting local search rankings.
        </li>
        <li>Clean, maintainable styles using Tailwind CSS.</li>
      </ul>
    </ProjectItem>
